# Image Management Configuration
# This file is created to ensure the images directory exists and is tracked by git

# Directory structure:
# /src/main/resources/images/          - Image metadata (YAML files)
# /src/main/resources/static/images/   - Actual image files
# /src/main/resources/static/images/thumbnails/ - Thumbnail files

# Configuration notes:
# - Maximum file size: 10MB
# - Supported formats: JPG, PNG, GIF, WebP, BMP
# - Thumbnails are automatically generated at 300px
# - Compression quality: 0.8 (80%)
# - Images are organized by categories
# - Metadata is stored in YAML format for easy management